article.headline: Stephen F.Austin 77, Howard Payne 38
article.story: NACOGDOCHES, Texas -- Josh Alexander, Matt Kingsley and Eddie Williams scored 16 points apiece to lead Stephen F. Austin to a 77-38 win over Howard Payne on Friday night. Tom Hermann led Howard Payne with 11 points. Howard Payne was 6 of 24 from the field for 25 percent in the first half, and Stephen F. Austin led 35-16 at the half.
